# FHI Color Guide, Limited Edition Color of the Year 2021

## A two-guide set for hard home and fashion accessories

Sku#: FHIP110COY21

$ 235.00$ 188.00

NOTIFY ME

The product is currently out of stock

Designed to show the appearance of color on product, the Fashion, Home + Interiors Color Guide is now available in a limited edition to celebrate Pantone Color of the Year 2021: PANTONE 17-5104 Ultimate Gray and PANTONE 13-0647 Illuminating, a marriage of color conveying a message of strength and hopefulness that is both enduring and uplifting. This special edition two-guide set features a beautiful soft-touch cover and comes in a decorative box. Inside, you’ll also find a full page of Ultimate Gray and Illuminating, more about why we selected the colors for 2021, and a complete history of the past Colors of the Year.

